reviewText:
Rarescope's FLICKS WITH KICKS 2 box set was cancelled and never released.
You'll have to buy these films individually or settle for the first Flicks With Kicks box set.

The films that would have been included were:

Love and Sword
Choi Lee Fut Kung Fu
Elimination Pursuit
Duel at Supreme Gate
Drunken Dragon
Cub Tiger of Kwang Tung
Along Comes the Tiger
Kings of Fists and Dollars

Est. Release Date: Jan 6, 2009
UPC: 787364825899
